{"type": "article", "id": 2214, "title": "四季主题花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:44:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222254FOkSEJojqRaXuVbn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">挪威设计师 Kristine Five Melvær 推出了一款以四季变换为主题的玻璃花瓶，第一个花瓶的灵感来自春天的樱花和绿叶，第二个花瓶试图表现潜入夏天的大海里面洗海澡与冲浪的感觉，第三个花瓶以秋叶落满大地的场景为灵感，第四个则诠释了冬天雪花轻轻飘落在地面的情景。整个花瓶采取人工吹制的技术，使得每个图案都是独一无二的。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134929czAfMNypd3Xt5a9l.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134930Yro2E6JDIT3q7sfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134930fU8PoWk2Y9wME3Kl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134931PEdGIMLm7sYVZt81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}